*fcron-3.0.6-r3 (29 Aug 2012)

  29 Aug 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +fcron-3.0.6-r3.ebuild,
  +files/fcron.init.3, +files/fcrontab.2, -fcron-3.0.5-r2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Remove old. Add new ebuild that avoid spitting pages-long documentation and
  instead relies on users knowing what they are doing and use pkg_config to set
  up the package with its systab. Do not change files' permissions at postinst
  time as that's bad practice.

  24 May 2012; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> fcron-3.0.5-r2.ebuild,
  fcron-3.0.6-r1.ebuild, fcron-3.0.6-r2.ebuild:
  Inherit flag-o-matic for append-flags, and user for enewuser/etc...

